                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="pertanyaan-tentang-bullying-beserta-intruksi">
                            19. pertanyaan tentang bullying beserta intruksi</h2><br />
                        <p>What must we do to stop bullying at school?</p><p>Belows are steps to stop bullying at school:
</p><p>1. Stand up for people who are bullied. Bullies often want an audience and approval.
</p><p>2. Take an anti-bullying pledge. Print out our pledge to stand up against bullying.
</p><p>3. Take action.
</p><p>4. Talk to other kids.
</p><p>5. Talk to your teachers or principal.
</p><p>6. Talk to your parents or guardians.  </p><p>7. Speak (and write) up!  </p><p>8. Get creative.</p><br />
